---
const lastUpdated = 'February 27, 2026';
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50/30 to-purple-50/30 dark:from-slate-900 dark:via-slate-900/80 dark:to-slate-900/50"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-72 h-72 bg-sky-200/20 dark:bg-sky-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-200/20 dark:bg-purple-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/50 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-300 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
      </svg>
      Your privacy is our priority
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">
      Privacy
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600 via-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Policy</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
      We believe in plain language, not legal jargon. Here's exactly how we handle your data.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Policy Content -->
<section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Intro card -->
    <div class="bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-900/20 border border-sky-200 dark:border-sky-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="p-2 bg-sky-100 dark:bg-sky-900/50 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          EversPass ("we," "us," or "our") is operated by urielcookies Technologies. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data. By using EversPass, you agree to the practices described here.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sections -->
    <div class="space-y-12">

      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">1</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Information We Collect</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Account Information</h3>
            <p>When you create an account, we collect your email address and, optionally, your name. Authentication is handled securely via Clerk. We do not store passwords directly.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Photos and Media</h3>
            <p>Photos and videos you upload to sessions are stored temporarily on our servers for the duration of your session. They are automatically and permanently deleted upon session expiry. We do not retain copies.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Usage Data</h3>
            <p>We collect basic usage information such as session creation dates, file counts, and storage usage. This is used solely to provide and improve the service.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Guest Access</h3>
            <p>Guests who access sessions via a link do not need an account. We do not collect personal information from guests beyond standard server request logs (IP address, browser type, timestamp), which are used for security and abuse prevention.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">2</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Operate and maintain the EversPass service</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Enforce our storage limits and plan features</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Send transactional emails (receipts, account notifications)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Detect and prevent abuse or unauthorized use</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Improve and develop new features</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">We do <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">not</strong> sell your data to third parties. We do not use your photos to train AI or machine learning models. We do not display advertising.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">3</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Data Sharing</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <p>We share your data only with trusted service providers necessary to operate EversPass:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 ml-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Clerk</strong> — authentication and user account management</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Stripe</strong> — payment processing (we never see your card details)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Railway</strong> — cloud hosting for our backend and database</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>Each provider is contractually bound to handle your data responsibly and in accordance with applicable law. We do not share data with any other third parties.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">4</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Data Retention & Deletion</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <div class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/20 border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-800/50 rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-800 dark:text-emerald-300">Photos and media are automatically deleted when a session expires. We never retain your photos beyond the session duration.</p>
          </div>
          <p>Account information (email, name, billing history) is retained for as long as you have an account. If you delete your account, all data is permanently removed within 30 days.</p>
          <p>To request deletion of your account and all associated data, email <a href="mailto:privacy@everspass.com" class="text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400 hover:underline">privacy@everspass.com</a> or use the account settings page.</p>
          <p>Server logs (IP addresses, request timestamps) are retained for up to 90 days for security purposes, then automatically deleted.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">5</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Security</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <p>We take security seriously. All data is transmitted over HTTPS (TLS encryption). Passwords are managed through Clerk and never stored in plain text. Payment data is handled entirely by Stripe — we do not store card numbers.</p>
          <p>Sessions are only accessible via their unique link. They are not publicly listed, indexed, or searchable. Access is scoped to anyone with the link, which you control.</p>
          <p>While we implement industry-standard protections, no system is 100% secure. If you discover a security issue, please email us at <a href="mailto:security@everspass.com" class="text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400 hover:underline">security@everspass.com</a> and we'll respond promptly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">6</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Cookies</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <p>We use minimal cookies necessary to operate the service. These include:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Authentication cookies</strong> — to keep you logged into your account (set by Clerk)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-sky-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Session storage</strong> — local browser storage for temporary session data</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or any third-party analytics that collect personal information.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 7 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">7</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Your Rights</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Access</strong> — request a copy of your data</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Correction</strong> — update inaccurate information</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Deletion</strong> — request removal of your account and data</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Portability</strong> — export your data in a usable format</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:privacy@everspass.com" class="text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-400 hover:underline">privacy@everspass.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 8 -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200/80 dark:border-slate-800/80 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white">8</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we'll update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. For significant changes, we'll notify registered users via email.</p>
          <p>Your continued use of EversPass after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-sky-900/20 dark:to-purple-900/20 border border-sky-200 dark:border-sky-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Questions About Privacy?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6">We're happy to explain anything in plain English. Don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
        <a href="mailto:privacy@everspass.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-600 to-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl hover:from-sky-700 hover:to-blue-700 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z"></path>
            <path d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z"></path>
          </svg>
          privacy@everspass.com
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
